data.description: Back on market - buyer's financing fell through **Seller-paid RATE BUY-DOWN OPTION and home sold with Design Services Included!!** Seller will entertain possible interest rate buy down or closing cost credit (up to 2% of purchase price) with acceptable offer! If you need more room for everyone, you found it - welcome home to Bartram Park Preserve. This Mattamy-built home is move-in ready, just for you, offering four spacious bedrooms, an additional loft space upstairs, and an office/flex room downstairs. So many possibilities! From the moment you walk inside, you're welcomed by the classic open banister railing leading upstairs. You'll love the natural light that abounds in every room. A walk through the large foyer leads you to the gourmet kitchen boasting double wall ovens, white shaker cabinets, and quartz countertops with an expansive contrasting island. The bright and open floorplan offers seamless living and dining spaces for endless entertaining, while the upstairs bedrooms offer optimal privacy. Once upstairs, you'll find a loft, 3 secondary bedrooms (2 with walk-in closets), conveniently located oversized laundry room, a shared bathroom with abundant vanity space and tiled shower, and a spacious owner's suite. Your primary suite is a relaxing escape at the end of the day offering an eye-catching cove ceiling, massive walk-in closet, and well-appointed luxury bath with double vanity sinks, separate soaking tub, frameless glass enclosure custom tile shower, and separate water closet. Throughout the home you'll find a fresh coat of paint, faux wood window blinds, hardwired alarm system, and pre-wired Cat 5 outlets with a central hub for your modem. Home also includes a whole-house water softener and additional on-demand reverse osmosis water filtration system at the kitchen sink. The entire first floor offers durable and timeless wood-look tile. This home has so much space and so much to offer, all located in the desirable Bartram area - close to shopping, dining, great schools, and easy access to I-95 and I-295 for a stress-free commute. The Bartram Park Preserve neighborhood offers community pool with children's splash pad play area, well-appointed fitness center, a dog park, various sports fields, and multiple playgrounds throughout the community. Schedule your tour today and let's make this one yours - nothing to do but move right in! (For 2/1 buy down concession, use preferred local lender, Bank of England. Contact Troy Silhan for more information.)
